<div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Discover Feni</h1>
    
    <!-- Feni Overview Section -->
    <div class="bg-light text-dark p-4 rounded shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="text-center">What is Feni?</h2>
        <p class="lead text-center">
            Feni is a traditional Goan spirit made from the fermentation of coconut sap or cashew apples. This unique drink reflects the essence of Goa, offering a rich and vibrant flavor that encapsulates the spirit of the region.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Feni Production Process Section -->
    <div class="my-4">
        <h2 class="text-center">Production Process</h2>
        <ul class="list-group">
            <li class="list-group-item bg-dark text-light">1. <strong>Harvesting</strong>: Fresh coconut sap or cashew apples are harvested.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item bg-dark text-light">2. <strong>Fermentation</strong>: The sap or juice undergoes natural fermentation for several days.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item bg-dark text-light">3. <strong>Distillation</strong>: The fermented liquid is distilled in copper stills, enhancing the flavor.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item bg-dark text-light">4. <strong>Bottling</strong>: Finally, the distilled Feni is bottled for you to enjoy!</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- How to Enjoy Section -->
    <div class="bg-light text-dark p-4 rounded shadow-sm my-4">
        <h2 class="text-center">How to Enjoy Feni</h2>
        <p class="text-center">
            Feni can be enjoyed in various ways:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-unstyled text-center">
            <li><strong>Neat</strong>: Enjoy the authentic flavor by sipping it straight.</li>
            <li><strong>With Mixers</strong>: Try it with tonic water, soda, or juices.</li>
            <li><strong>In Cocktails</strong>: Experiment with our cocktail recipes to create delicious drinks!</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Video Section -->
<div class="text-center my-4">
    <video controls autoplay muted class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm" width="640" height="360">
        <source src="images/feni-making.mp4" type="video/mp4">
        Your browser does not support the video tag.
    </video>
</div>


